        //The feathers fly part 1
        addSound("[1/7] ???: Oh?! Hold on, is anyone there..!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-1", true);
        addSound("[2/7] Ava: Why hello there! Whatcha doin' here? I'm Ava!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-2", true);
        addSound("[3/7] Ava: Want a quick job? How 'bout helpin' me out?! That was perfect timing!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-3", true);
        addSound("[4/7] Ava: Y'see, while the other Avos hate it, I just find electromagic so fascinating!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-4", true);
        addSound("[5/7] Ava: Look, I think I got a breakthrough invention. If it works... Oh man...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-5", true);
        addSound("[6/7] Ava: I just need to harness some nature magic, and there's an amazing source in the chief's hut. Ya comin'?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-6", true);
        addSound("[7/7] Ava: Don't you worry about rewards! I got you! See ya' there!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-7", true);
        addSound("[1/6] Ava: Hey! You showed up! Listen up, here's the plan...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-8", true);
        addSound("[2/6] Ava: There's a small museum inside the hut with all kinds of trophies.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-9", true);
        addSound("[3/6] Ava: Our chief is quite the talkative fella, and I can guarantee he'd love to tell you stories.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-10", true);
        addSound("[4/6] Ava: That should keep him and his guards busy. And that's where I come in!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-11", true);
        addSound("[5/6] Ava: I'll take that chance to sneak behind the throne, where our sacred totem is. I'm not stealing it, don't worry!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-12", true);
        addSound("[6/6] Ava: I'm a little clumsy, but I'm sure I can count on ya'! No matter what, keep the chief busy!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-13", true);
        addSound("[1/5] Avos Chieftain: Greetings, human. Welcome back.", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-1", true);
        addSound("[2/5] Avos Chieftain: So, what brings you here, hm?", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-2", true);
        addSound("[3/5] Avos Chieftain: Oh, you want to learn more about us... Of course, of course!", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-3", true);
        addSound("[4/5] Avos Chieftain: We have a room where I can show you some of our history.", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-4", true);
        addSound("[5/5] Avos Chieftain: You're in luck, I'm in a good mood. Follow me then.", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-5", true);
        addSound("[1/2] Avos Chief: Ah, history first! Great, great!", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-1", true);
        addSound("[1/2] Avos Chief: Gah! You startled me!", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-2", true);
        addSound("[1/3] Avos Chief: Ah, our wisteria tree! Yes...", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-3", true);
        addSound("[1/2] Avos Chief: Oh, this is quite the important tome.", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-4", true);
        addSound("[1/2] Avos Chief: Right, the feathery crate!", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-5", true);
        addSound("[1/1] Avos Chieftain: What was that?! I'll check.", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-6", true);
        addSound("[1/2] Avos Chieftain: Someone broke in? But why? Anyone can use our totem...", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-7", true);
        addSound("[2/2] Avos Chieftain: I don't get it. They could've just asked...", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-8", true);
        addSound("[1/7] Ava: Oh, hey! Thanks for earlier. You were a big help.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-14", true);
        addSound("[2/7] Ava: Truth is, anyone can use that totem. They just don't like me very much.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-15", true);
        addSound("[3/7] Ava: Anyway, we got what we needed, and it's promising! Now onto the next part...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-16", true);
        addSound("[4/7] Ava: Y'see, I managed to bottle up some of our magic, but I still need Corkian stuff.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-17", true);
        addSound("[5/7] Ava: Fortunately for us, there's a shop outside the city. Though, things might get complicated...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-18", true);
        addSound("[6/7] Ava: A bunch of Corkians aren't too fond of... Us. I just think you should come along with me, y'know?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-19", true);
        addSound("[7/7] Ava: Here, I wrote the coords into that book of yours. It's a bit far, so come on out and I'll give you a lift!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-20", true);
        addSound("[1/2] Ava: Alright, if you want a lift, tell me, or you could just walk!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-21", true);
