        addSound("[1/3] Shopkeeper: Huh?! I made myself clear! You were with her!", "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-5", true);
        addSound("[2/3] Shopkeeper: I'm closing for today, I cannot stand this! OUT!!", "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-6", true);
        addSound("[3/3] Shopkeeper: Oh, and don't even think about even approaching MY shop!", "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-7", true);
        addSound("[1/1] Ava: Hang tight! He's gone crazy!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-40", true);
        addSound("[1/7] Ava: Urgh, this guy's nuts. Hmm...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-41", true);
        addSound("[2/7] Ava: I'm... surprised he kicked you out, too. Maybe he's a patriot?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-42", true);
        addSound("[3/7] Ava: Well, anyway, we need a plan. I don't wanna wait this out.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-43", true);
        addSound("[4/7] Ava: Look, this guy has to have a control panel somewhere. Maybe we can neutralize the robots.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-44", true);
        addSound("[5/7] Ava: That stuff hates water, y'know? So I'll go fetch some in the meantime.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-45", true);
        addSound("[6/7] Ava: I'd like to NOT get zapped by a forcefield, so I'll sneak inside once we're done with that.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-46", true);
        addSound("[7/7] Ava: Got it? Find the control panel. It should be somewhere around the house. Talk to me once you're ready.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-47", true);
        addSound("[1/1] Ava: Good luck, then! I'll be back once you find the control panel and get inside!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-48", true);
        addSound("[1/5] Ava: Here we are! Good job! Alright, let's see...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-49", true);
        addSound("[2/5] Ava: Wait... Why are there... Buttons... Everywhere??", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-50", true);
        addSound("[3/5] Ava: I feel like soaking everything would be quite the mistake.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-51", true);
        addSound("[4/5] Ava: And none of them are labelled! What is that?!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-52", true);
        addSound("[5/5] Ava: Look, your choice. What should we neutralize first?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-53", true);
        addSound("[1/2] Ava: Left, huh? Well, let's see how that goes.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-54", true);
        addSound("[2/2] Ava: Alright, let's soak this.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-55", true);
        addSound("!safetyteleportationsequenceactivated!", "thefeathersflypart1-security-1", true);
        addSound("[1/1] Ava: TELEPORTATION?!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-56", true);
        addSound("[1/5] Ava: Center... I guess the most important stuff could be here. In theory. I wouldn't count on it.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-57", true);
        addSound("[2/5] Ava: Huh! This wasn't that bad. And... I see something poking out, hold on...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-58", true);
        addSound("[3/5] Ava: Haha! I think that's what we're looking for!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-59", true);
        addSound("[4/5] Ava: Look, I still want to make it up to the guy. I really don't want to be the villain of his story.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-60", true);
        addSound("[5/5] Ava: I'll meet you back at the Workshop. You can go on ahead.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-61", true);
        addSound("[1/4] Ava: Right, right. Stand back, just in case.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-62", true);
        addSound("! ERROR: Defense protocols shutdown!", "thefeathersflypart1-security-2", true);
        addSound("[2/4] Ava: Oh wow. You got the right one, first try! How'd you know?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-63", true);
        addSound("[3/4] Ava: Well, good job. I still want to make it up to the poor guy though.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-64", true);
        addSound("[4/4] Ava: Just meet me back at the Workshop, I'll be there!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-65", true);
        addSound("[1/4] Ava: Ouch!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-66", true);
        addSound("[2/4] Ava: Sorry about all the trouble I caused... I hope this makes it up to you.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-67", true);
        addSound("[3/4] Ava: I hope that human's alright... I managed to find the microchip right away, after all.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-68", true);
        addSound("[4/4] Ava: ...Alright. Time to go. I'll wait for them, I guess.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-69", true);
        addSound("[1/3] Ava: Ouch!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-70", true);
        addSound("[2/3] Ava: Sorry about all the trouble I caused... I hope this makes it up to you.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-71", true);
        addSound("[3/3] Ava: ...Alright. Time to go.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-72", true);
        addSound("[1/2] Ava: Oh, there you are! I felt sad leaving you behind!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-73", true);
        addSound("[2/2] Ava: Say, if you need a lift, just tell me.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-74", true);
        addSound("[1/1] Ava: Alright then, buckle up!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-75", true);
        addSound("[1/1] Ava: Alright, I'm dropping you off! Stick the landing!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-76", true);
        addSound("[1/7] Ava: I can't believe it! It's working! Look! Look at it!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-77", true);
        addSound("[2/7] Ava: A Growth Accelerator... Can you imagine the possibilities?!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-78", true);
        addSound("[3/7] Ava: We'll be able to... I don't know, help the poor, that's nice, right?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-79", true);
        addSound("[4/7] Ava: But we're not done. Well, I'm not done. I'd still like your help.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-80", true);
        addSound("[5/7] Ava: Look, let's try it out together, alright? Maybe I'll let you go afterwards?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-81", true);
        addSound("[6/7] Ava: I'll join you outside. Once I'm sure this works, I'll be able to... Show it to them.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-82", true);
        addSound("[7/7] Ava: In theory, it should be easy to operate... I'm trusting you. Again. Sorry 'bout that.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-83", true);
        addSound("[1/2] Ava: Alright, it's just on the hill next to us, but I can bring you there if ya want!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-84", true);
        addSound("[2/2] Ava: Just don't get too used to me, alright? Tell me when you're ready.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-85", true);
        addSound("[1/1] Ava: Here we go!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-86", true);
